            , JUN. On the 15th of June, I had a basket of peas in my cart, which stood in <placeName id="t18220703-85-crimeloc443">Covent Garden-market</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18220703-85-crimeloc443" type="placeName" value="Covent Garden-market"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18220703-85-crimeloc443" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220703-85-off441 t18220703-85-crimeloc443"></join>, close to the Piazza - and at half-past three o'clock in the morning I missed it. I attend the market for 
               <persName id="t18220703-85-person757">
                  John 
                  Hierons
               <interp inst="t18220703-85-person757" type="surname" value="Hierons"></interp>
